comments: Turner (IND) makes marginal contact to Doncic's (DAL) at the start of his drive to the basket.
Nesmith (IND) and Doncic (DAL) mutually engage in marginal contact as both players position themselves to rebound the ball.
Nembhard (IND) gathers the ball on his right foot and slides it prior to releasing his shot attempt.
Nesmith (IND) jumps up with the ball still in his hand and lands before releasing his dribble.
Nembhard (IND) rests his hand on Bullock's (DAL) front and both players engage in marginal contact as Bullocks sets the pick.
Bullock (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Haliburton's (IND) drive toward the rim.
Haliburton (IND) leads unnaturally with his knee and delivers contact to Keleber's (DAL) front and affects his ability to defend the driving shot attempt.
Nesmith (IND) makes contact to the ball prior to making marginal side to side contact with Irving (DAL) on the shot near the rim.
Nesmith (IND) is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession was correctly awarded to Dallas.
Turner (IND) steps slightly in Doncic's (DAL) path and the contact at the start of Doncic's drive is marginal.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Doncic (DAL) is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession was correctly awarded to Indiana.
